<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.3.6">
<l>pāṇṭavar tammuṭaiya pāñcālima ṟukkamellām</l>
<l>āṇṭaṅku nūṟṟuvartam peṇṭirmēlvait tavappaṉmalai</l>
<l>pāṇtaku vaṇṭiṉaṅkaḷ paṇkaḷpāṭima tupparuka</l>
<l>tōṇṭalu ṭaiyamalai tollaimāliruñ cōlaiyatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain of [our] father who, in that very time and place,</l>
<l rend="indent">placed upon the wives of the hundred</l>
<l rend="indent">all the distress of Pāñcāli, [wife] of the Pāṇḍavas,</l>
<l>that is ancient Māliruñcōlai,</l>
<l rend="indent">the mountain that has deep spring wells</l>
<l rend="indent">so that swarms of bees, worthy of song,</l>
<l rend="indent">sing melodies and drink honey.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
